DisplayedText.SourceString: LORD MORGRUMP ATTACKING THE QUEEN IN HER THRONE ROOM!
DisplayedText.LocalizedString: LORD MORGRUMP ATTACKING THE QUEEN IN HER THRONE ROOM!

DisplayedText.SourceString: TERRIBLE BUSINESS. HEAD TO THE CASTLE AS QUICKLY AS YOU CAN AND MAKE SURE THE VISION DOES NOT COME TRUE!
DisplayedText.LocalizedString: TERRIBLE BUSINESS. HEAD TO THE CASTLE AS QUICKLY AS YOU CAN AND MAKE SURE THE VISION DOES NOT COME TRUE!

DisplayedText.SourceString: NOW, I HAVE A POTION THAT MAY HELP YOU OUT AT A VERY PARTICULAR... JUNCTURE. MOONBEARD CAN SAY NO MORE! STIR THE POTION AND DRINK UP, LAD!
DisplayedText.LocalizedString: NOW, I HAVE A POTION THAT MAY HELP YOU OUT AT A VERY PARTICULAR... JUNCTURE. MOONBEARD CAN SAY NO MORE! STIR THE POTION AND DRINK UP, LAD!

DisplayedText.SourceString: AH, YOUNG LATCH... LISTEN TO THIS! LAST NIGHT I HAD A VISION...
DisplayedText.LocalizedString: AH, YOUNG LATCH... LISTEN TO THIS! LAST NIGHT I HAD A VISION...

Text.CultureInvariantString: LORD MORGRUMP ATTACKING THE QUEEN IN HER THRONE ROOM!

TERRIBLE BUSINESS. HEAD TO THE CASTLE AS QUICKLY AS YOU 
CAN AND MAKE SURE THE VISION DOES NOT COME TRUE!

NOW, I HAVE A POTION THAT MAY HELP YOU OUT AT A VERY 
PARTICULAR... JUNCTURE. MOONBEARD CAN SAY NO MORE! 
STIR THE POTION AND DRINK UP, LAD!

AH, YOUNG LATCH... LISTEN TO THIS! 
LAST NIGHT I HAD A VISION...
